{"word":"Groves","slug":"groves","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Groves</b> Sometimes translated Asherod, Ashera, and Asherim.<br/> Symbols of the Phenician goddess, Ashera<br/> <a href='S:Ashtoreth'>Ashtoreth</a><br/> Forbidden to be established<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=21'>Deu 16:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=1&verse=29'>Isa 1:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=17&verse=8'>Isa 17:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=27&verse=9'>Isa 27:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=5&verse=14'>Mic 5:14</a><br/> Worshiped by Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=3&verse=7'>Jdg 3:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=15'>1Ki 14:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=23'>1Ki 14:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=13'>1Ki 15:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=19'>1Ki 18:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=13&verse=6'>2Ki 13:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=10'>2Ki 17:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=16'>2Ki 17:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=21&verse=7'>2Ki 21:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=24&verse=18'>2Ch 24:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=17&verse=2'>Jer 17:2</a><br/> Destroyed by:<br/> - Gideon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=28'>Jdg 6:28</a> <br/> - Hezekiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=18&verse=4'>2Ki 18:4</a> <br/> - Josiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=14'>2Ki 23:14</a>